[[File:FIG 2015 - Bruno Fuligni 02.jpg|thumbnail|Bruno Fuligni during International Festival of Geography 2015 in [[Saint-Dié-des-Vosges]].]] '''Bruno Fuligni''' (born 21 May 1968) is a [[French language|French]] writer and historian.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.franceinter.fr/emissions/le-nouveau-rendez-vous/le-nouveau-rendez-vous-26-juin-2018 |title=Micha Lescot et Bruno Fuligni |language=fr |date=June 26, 2018 |website=ranceinter.fr |accessdate=August 19, 2018 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.popmatters.com/the-case-of-alan-turing-2495411366.html |title='The Case of Alan Turing' Gives the Enigma Project the Graphic Treatment |date=October 26, 2016 |author=Sarah Boslaugh |publisher=''[[PopMatters]]'' |accessdate=August 19, 2018}}</ref>
